    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Projection prints that are of very high quality and made for screening at special events, such as gala premieres. Usually printed directly from the composited camera negative onto a higher quality of print stock than is usual for mass-production release prints.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
